本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:曾於娟研究生(外文):Tsengyuchuan論文名稱:司馬光《家範》 之校訂及其影響研究論文名稱(外文):A study on the revision of Guang Sima's  Book 〝Jia Fan〞 and the impact of the book指導教授:楊晉龍學位類別:碩士校院名稱:臺北市立教育大學系所名稱:中國語文學系碩士班學門:人文學門學類:中國語文學類論文出版年:2013畢業學年度:101語文別:中文論文頁數:273中文關鍵詞:《家範》、司馬光、家訓、九年一貫教育政策、家庭教育、家政教育、性別平等教育相關次數:

被引用:0點閱:646評分:下載:74書目收藏:1



   「家訓」產生在「家」(家庭、家族)的範疇中，記載長輩對後代子孫為人處事上的期許與規範，因此是瞭解古代家長治家、家庭教育等內容的重要管道。宋代是家訓發展繁盛的時期，產生許多家訓專著，司馬光《家範》當是其中影響較大的一本，本文即在前人既有的研究基礎上，針對此書進行更廣泛的研究，除探析其特色、內容、思想、流傳之外，更註重此書對後代的影響及其對現代教育的啟示等，以豐富家訓研究的成果。本文共分成六章：    第一章〈緒論〉：討論「家訓」之意，確立研究的動機與主題，說明研究的內容及目的與功能。並針對論及家訓、司馬光、《家範》等相關研究文獻進行必要的探討。    第二章〈《家範》版本內容考述〉：由於《家範》有多個版本流傳，故本章說明臺灣現存版本的狀況並進行比對，分析各版本的內容實況以確定最佳的研究文本。    第三章〈《家範》的成書〉：首先梳理時代、作者、家訓發展的情況，接著分析《家範》的分捲、分篇方式及其寫作特色，並探討司馬光《居家雜儀》與〈訓儉示康〉等兩部家訓作品與《家範》的關係，以增進對司馬光家訓思想的理解。   第四章〈《家範》內容與思想探究〉：以《家範》篇捲編排的順序為原則，詳細分析其內容，並歸納司馬光在治家和家庭教育上的重要思想。同時探討在性別區分下，《家範》呈現的兩性角色之面貌。   第五章〈《家範》的影響與現代教育〉：從「家範」一詞的溯源，探究《家範》自宋到清的流傳情形及其在歷史上的傳播狀況。擴及與臺灣現代教育相關議題的內容，藉由《家庭教育法》、〈國民中小學九年一貫課程綱要重大議題(家政教育)〉、《性別平等教育法》、〈國民中小學九年一貫課程綱要重大議題(性別平等教育)〉等內容的探討，分析《家範》對現今教育政策的啟示。   第六章〈結論〉：除說明《家範》研究結果的意義與功能外，還反思研究結果對教育有哪些可能的啟發，最後則對研究結果進行檢討，並提出未來更進一步研究的瞻望與可能性。

    Family instructions are the ways of dealing with people and situations written by family elders. These family instructions then passes down to their off spring. Therefore, these documents are the vital way for understanding family management and education mission in ancient times. Song dynasty is a prosperous period of creating family instructions. Sima Guang’s Book〝Jia Fan〞 in one of the family instructions has greater influence among others. This study extends the study category base on predecessors established research. In addition to study Jia-Fan’s main features, ideology and how it hand down to generations. This research makes further study on the impact to later generations and the influence to modern education.This research divides into six chapters.First chapter: Introduction.    Defining the concept of family instructions and clarifies the aim, objectives and key issues of this research. In this chapter, the literature review of family instruction, Sima Guang and 〝Jia Fan〞 are studied.Second chapter: The comparison and analysis of various editions of 〝Jia Fan〞.    Due to several editions of 〝Jia Fan〞 were in circulation, this chapter aim to compare the existing versions for determining the best edition for this study.Third chapter: How 〝Jia Fan〞 is written and edited    In this chapter, the development of family instructions and the analysis of how Siam Gang formed this family instructions and the characteristic of 〝Jia Fan〞 are studied. Furthermore, in order to understand more deeply about Siam Guang’s thought, his other two family instructions 〝Chu chia Za yi〞 and 〝Xun Jian Shi Kang 〞were explored.Forth chapter: The study of 〝Jia Fan〞    More deeply study of family management, educational mission and the presentation of both genders in 〝Jia Fan〞 are studied in this chapter.Fifth chapter: The impact of 〝Jia Fan〞 on modern education    To analyze the impact and inspiration from 〝Jia Fan〞 to today's education policy by research issues such as Family Education Law, Grade 1-9 Curriculum Guidelines-Home Economics Education, Gender Equality Education Act, Grade 1-9 Curriculum Guidelines-Gender Equality Education.Six chapters: Conclusion    In addition to demonstrate the meaning and impact of 〝Jia Fan〞, the result of this research reflects on the inspiration to today’s education. Furthermore, the examination of this research brings out the possible direction for subsequent research.

